@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Air Transport Company Collaborator" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC

ATCC -> System : Requests to list company fleet by age

activate System
System --> ATCC : Requests company and age criteria
deactivate System

ATCC -> System : Provides company identification and age criteria

activate System
System --> System : Check if collaborator is authorized
System --> System : Validate air transport company
System --> System : Check if collaborator belongs to company
System --> System : Validate age criteria
System --> System : Retrieve company fleet
System --> System : Calculate age for each aircraft
System --> System : Filter and/or order aircraft by age

alt matching aircraft exist
    System --> ATCC : Display fleet by age
else no matching aircraft exist
    System --> ATCC : Display empty list message
else user is not authorized or criteria are invalid
    System --> ATCC : Display error message
end

deactivate System
deactivate ATCC

@enduml